Visualization Module

PetalModule
- dynamically load javascript file

PetalInteraction
- unify mobile touch and computer mouse event (PetalMobileInteraction)
- simulate event:
    combo click,
    mouse holding,
    mouse selecting frame,
and mouse gesture
- PetalInteraction(callback) =>
    callback.comboclick   => function
    callback.mousehold    => function
    callback.mouseframe   => function
    callback.mousegesture => function

PetalMobileInteraction
- map mobile touch to computer mouse event
    touchstart          => mousedown
    touchmove           => mousemove
    touchend            => mouseup
    touchstart+touchend => click
                     *2 => dblclick
- simulate event:
    touch pinch
- PetalMobileInteraction(callback) =>
    callback.touchpinch   => function
